    <bcl:section id="d2e24" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Power under the <in:doc>Emergency Service Act</in:doc></bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The Thompson-Nicola Regional District is granted as an extended service the same power that a municipality has as a local authority under the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96111_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Emergency Program Act</in:doc></bcl:link> for such electoral area or areas the regional district may designate.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions of the <in:doc>Local Government Act</in:doc>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 323, relevant to the enactment of this regulation: section 799]</reg:provisionsnote>
